casebody.data:
Elisio Atenia LORENZO, Petitioner,
v.
Matthew G. WHITAKER, Acting Attorney General, Respondent. No. 15-70814 United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Filed January 17, 2019

ORDER

The opinion filed August 29, 2018, and reported at 902 F.3d 930 , is WITHDRAWN . A substitute memorandum disposition is filed concurrently with this order.

The government's petition for panel rehearing, filed November 14, 2018 (Dkt. 83), is DENIED .

The government's motion for judicial notice, filed November 14, 2018 (Dkt. 84), is DENIED .

No further petitions for rehearing en banc may be filed.
